'''Amagraman''' ('''Dittrichia viscosa''') d imγi iḥemlen imeṭqan i yetuneddan. Imusnawen n yimγan, qqaren-ed, belli seg Lazi i yed-itac, akken ad yaγ iri n yilel agrakal akked  Lurup neγ amadal s umata. Imγi n umagraman ittak anzi γer ''buzduz'' akked ''taysa'': Ad iṣbeḥ seg yiwet n txerrubt i yed-cetlen. Iferrawen n umagraman d izegzawen. Tizegzewt nsen ḥemqet. Mayella d talγa nsen truḥ s teγzef. Teγzef i yettuferyen afray n tuγmest.
